data.description: PRICE REDUCTION AND A $7500 SELLER'S CONCESSION ON FULL PRICE OFFER! Come tour this 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms home spanning 1,758 square feet of modern living. This MOVE IN READY property has a lot of natural lighting and an open living space highlighted by the kitchen, boasts wrap-around GRANITE COUNTERTOPS, a spacious island, EXTENDED KITCHEN CABINETS & COUNTERTOPS. Relax and entertain on the EXTENDED LANAI, enjoying the picturesque outdoor space & WATER VIEW. The master suite is a retreat for comfort & relaxation, complete with his and her closets. Located on a desirable lot with NON BUILDABLE LOT to the west, this property offers an ABUNDANCE OF OUTDOOR SPACE, creating a serene haven for your outdoor pleasures. Enjoy the community's resort style pool with a playground, basketball court, tennis court, and sidewalks for your walking, running or biking enjoyment!  This is an opportunity to embrace an extraordinary lifestyle - contact us today to make this exceptional property your new home. ALL WRITTEN OFFERS WILL BE PRESENTED!
